The paper proposes two different approaches for grade-aware course recommendation, which involves using representation learning techniques and grade prediction methods. This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), computer engineering (cs.CE), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
